<h2 style="color:tomato ">COVID-19</h2>
<p style="color:dodgerblue;">CORONA VIRUS OUTBREAK</p>
<p>The coronavirus is a family of viruses that can cause a range of illnesses in humans including common cold and more severe forms like SARS and MERS which are life-threatening. The virus is named after its shape which takes the form of a crown with protrusions around it and hence is known as coronavirus.</p>
